    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fcaf0000000000ea1a15",
      "text": "[K#F85E/0758-D053 https://dlt.kitetu.com/KNo.F85E/0758-D053][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449605,
      "updated": 1778529154
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fccd0000000000ea1a17",
      "text": " 研究開発を成功させるには15年くらいかかるという説",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449634,
      "updated": 1778449789
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fd4d0000000000ea1a1c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449763,
      "updated": 1778449763
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fcd00000000000ea1a18",
      "text": "[吉野彰]氏",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449638,
      "updated": 1778449737
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fca90000000000ea1a13",
      "text": " 「ダーウィンの海」についての一考察　リチウムイオン電池発明から市場形成まで",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449599,
      "updated": 1778449725
    },
    {
      "id": "6a00fd270000000000ea1a1b",
      "text": "  https://web.archive.org/web/20210904102135/https://www.jst.go.jp/tt/journal/journal_contents/2017/12/1712-10_article.html",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778449725,
      "updated": 1778449832
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0229210000000000b8076f",
      "text": "   この「関心はあるけど買わないよ」というのは本当にある[hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778526519,
      "updated": 1778526749
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0229570000000000b80771",
      "text": "    [デライト]の場合は「面白そうだけど使わないよ」だった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778526573,
      "updated": 1778526591
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0229630000000000b80772",
      "text": "     デライト宣伝は割と序盤から手応えは良くて、たくさんの人が「面白そう」と言ってくれた",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778526585,
      "updated": 1778526660
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0229960000000000b80773",
      "text": "      ただ、「面白そう」から先に進まなかった",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778526636,
      "updated": 1778526702
    },
